<h2 id='recommendations'>Recommendations</h2>
<p>1、For data information of market type, it is recommended to use WebSocket to receive real time data and conduct cache operation on data received.</p>

<p>2、For retrieving latest market price, it is recommended to use market.deals interface or subscribe deals.subscribe by using WebSocket.</p>
